  "prompt": "Which are the top architects in pune?",
  "response": "Pune has a vibrant architectural scene with numerous talented architects and firms. While it\u2019s challenging to list the absolute top architects definitively, here are some notable architects and firms known for their work in Pune:\n\n1. **Sanjay Puri Architects** - Known for innovative design and sustainable architecture, this firm has received numerous awards for its work.\n\n2. **Rohan Mehra Architects** - This firm has notable projects that reflect contemporary styles and efficiency.\n\n3. **Girish Nandkarni** - An architect with significant contributions to residential and commercial projects, focusing on modern design themes.\n\n4. **Input Zero** - A multidisciplinary design practice known for its innovative approach to architecture and urban design.\n\n5. **Chaitanya A. Narkhede** - An architect with a focus on combining modern architecture with traditional elements.\n\n6. **Studio H** - A firm that emphasizes sustainable design and integrates natural elements into their projects.\n\n7. **Kiran Kamble Architects** - Known for both residential and commercial projects, emphasizing context-appropriate design.\n\n8. **Aditi Narkhede** - Recognized for her work on residential projects characterized by modern aesthetics and functionality.\n\n9. **Himanshu Kumbhar Architects** - A firm known for creative solutions and a focus on client needs.\n\n10. **Morphogenesis** - Although based primarily in Delhi, they also have a strong presence and influence in Pune with significant projects.\n\nWhen considering an architect or firm, it's essential to look at their portfolio, design philosophy, and reviews from previous clients to see if their style aligns with your project needs.",
